<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>The agro spells are nice, but you HAVE to know how to use them. Most SKs I have met have no idea how they work. For instance....<br>
If you put your visage up, it doesn't do dick right off the bat. First, you have to taunt. THEN the taunt has to be successful. THEN it will add an increased number of points to your hate-listing, depending on which spell you use. The drawback about this spell is that it pops JUST before it wears off. This actually is best if the SK DOESN'T use it for himself. If the SK is going to tank, he is much better off using his jolts since they are instant agro and fast recast (yes, about 7 secs.) The visage is best used if it is used on <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline">ANOTHER toon</span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> that is tanking. THEN the taunt will add 5, 10, or whatever on each successful taunt instead of one.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
